    "content": "Artist: Calvin Harris\r\n  song: How Deep Is Your Love\r\n\r\n(Intro)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nD|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nA|-33---33-|-33---33-|-33---33-|-33---33-|\r\nE|---------|---------|---------|---------|  x 4[/tab]\r\n\r\nAah aah aah oo ooh, Aah aah aah oo ooh\r\n\r\nI want you to breathe me, let me be your air\r\n                 \r\nLet me roam your body freely, no inhibition, no fear\r\n\r\nHow deep is your love?\r\n\r\n(pattern 1)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nD|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nA|---------|-33---33-|-00---00-|-00---00-|\r\nE|-00---00-|---------|---------|---------|  x 2[/tab]\r\n\r\nIs it like the ocean? What devotion? Are you?\r\n                  \r\nHow deep is your love? Is it like nirvana?\r\n        \r\nHit me harder, again\r\n\r\n(pattern 2)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nD|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nA|-33---33-|-33---33-|-00---00-|-00---00-|\r\nE|---------|---------|---------|---------|  [/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nD|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nA|-33---33-|-33---33-|-00---00-|---------|\r\nE|---------|---------|---------|---------| [/tab]\r\n\r\nHow deep is your love? How deep is your love?\r\n                  \r\nHow deep is your love? Is it like the ocean?\r\n\r\nPull me closer, again\r\n\r\n(pattern 3)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nD|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nA|-77---77-|-33---33-|-00---00-|-00---00-|\r\nE|---------|---------|---------|---------|  x 2[/tab]\r\n\r\nHow deep is your love?\r\n                  \r\nHow deep is your love?\r\n\r\n(pattern 2b)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nD|---------|---------|---------|---------|\r\nA|-33---33-|-33---33-|-00---00-|-00---00-|\r\nE|---------|---------|---------|---------|  [/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|-------